Package com.example.myapplication.data.model

Class NotificationList

java.lang.Object
com.example.myapplication.data.model.NotificationList
public class NotificationList extends Object
This is a model for the NotificationList in Firestore Fields of notificationList document: - eventId: String - all: List This is a list of all users for notification purposes *Could possibly be changed* - cancelled: List This is a list of all users who chose not to accept the invitation from an event - invited: List This is a list of all users who are chosen by the lottery to sign up for an event - finalList: List This is a list of all users who have accepted the invitation to the event. - waiting: List This is a list of all users who are a part of the waiting list. This list gets updated as users are moved to the cancelled or final list.
